data.description: The Charm of this log home is unbelievable. 9+ acres lots of fruit trees, tons of wildlife (the elk winter here) wood heated shop several old barns from the original settlers, Giant 4 bay+ covered parking, open floor plan home with the most charming wood stove. New cabinets in the kitchen, log home is a solid well sealed beauty! Spiral stair case to the bedrooms. 3 bedrooms, 2 bath big laundry and a setting that is to die for. All on a county maintained road.
